Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain

Class Maze

java.lang.Object
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain.Maze
public class Maze extends Object
The Maze Class represents the state of the maze internally. It has methods for utility and modifying the maze, as well as standard getters and setters.
